title: Riot Kayle And icon
body: Idk why but i didn't get my riot kayle skin and i was really looking forward to it please help me.

replies.body: I'm in the same boat, least i k that i need to wait 1 week more

The gifts are still being sent out and has been extended to the 30th per our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Hang tight, and the goods will come!
